118
00:06:25,416 --> 00:06:27,875
that Twenty Faces
followers are using.

119
00:06:27,958 --> 00:06:30,083
There's a Twenty Faces
hashtag now?

120
00:06:30,166 --> 00:06:32,541
Yeah, and it's spreading
really quickly.

121
00:06:34,625 --> 00:06:36,958
[HASHIBA]
