124
00:06:41,791 --> 00:06:45,500
Look, this one even openly
names Akechi as their enemy.

125
00:06:45,583 --> 00:06:47,958
Right here, they call
themselves "Successor."

126
00:06:48,041 --> 00:06:49,458
[HASHIBA]
"Successor"?

127
00:06:49,541 --> 00:06:51,458
[KOBAYASHI] They say that this
person follows the wishes

128
00:06:51,541 --> 00:06:54,875
of the original Twenty Faces
from three years ago.

129
00:06:54,958 --> 00:06:57,875
They've been gaining
popularity with the fans.

130
00:06:57,958 --> 00:07:00,583
I wonder what
they're really like.

131
