I'm trying my best to solve
the Twenty Faces case,

139
00:07:23,541 --> 00:07:26,583
and I'm helping our friend,
Akechi, in the process.

140
00:07:26,666 --> 00:07:29,458
Don't you think those things are
more important than school?

141
