actions into the formula.

193
00:09:46,333 --> 00:09:47,833
Think about it.

194
00:09:47,916 --> 00:09:50,083
What's the most important piece
of the puzzle at this moment?

195
00:09:50,166 --> 00:09:53,958
It's you. It all hangs
on what you do next.

196
00:09:54,041 --> 00:09:55,833
It doesn't surprise me, though.

197
00:09:55,916 --> 00:09:58,583
It's just like you to exclude
yourself from a formula

198
00:09:58,666 --> 00:10:01,583
which is meant to represent
the whole world.

199
00:10:21,375 --> 00:10:23,541
